Walmart Rewards

Hey, thanks for asking about the weekend. I ended up rearranging the bookshelves – took hours but it looks way better now. I also found an old photo album from that trip we took a few years ago. It was fun to flip through and remember all the random adventures. The weather was perfect for it – cool and cloudy, so no glare on the windows. I might try to go for a walk later if the rain holds off. Let me know if you want to grab coffee on Tuesday instead of Thursday. I think my schedule is more open that day. Talk soon.

 

